{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_10_02",
  "title": "成宮すず 2話 私だけですわ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すず、新曲のテーマについてなんだが、調子はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ about the theme of the new song‚ how's it going?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、正直……ちょっと行き詰まっていますわ\nもっとすいすい進むものだと思っていたのですけれど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Umm… to be honest‚ we're a bit stuck.\nI thought it would be going smoothly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "初めは、四人で活動する中で感じてきたことを\nテーマにしよう……という話になりましたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At first‚ we decided the theme would be about\nwhat we felt while working as the four of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.8333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、いざ一つのテーマに決めようとしても\nいろいろな想いが溢れ過ぎてしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ when we tried to pick just one theme\nwe realized there were so many memories…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.5666673024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな、アイデアがないんじゃなくて\n多過ぎてかえってまとまらないのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. It’s not a lack of ideas‚ but having\ntoo many ideas made it hard to organize.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら……例えば、何か一つの\nキーワードを考えてみるのもいいかもしれないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then…… for example‚\nmaybe it would help to come up with a keyword.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "キーワード……ですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A keyword……?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.5666673024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "四人で練習やライブバトルをしている時\nみんなが常に考えていることはないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When the four of you practiced or did live battles‚\nwasn’t there something you were all thinking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "何か一つ重要な言葉を設定して\nそれを軸に考えてみるのはどうか……と思ってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought‚ how about choosing\nan important keyword and brainstorming based on that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.0333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。切り口を一つに絞ってみるんですわね\nうーん、それなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ so it’s about narrowing things down to one perspective.\nHmm‚ then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "私は……いえ、私だけでなく、渚も沙季も、芽衣も……\n去っていった琴乃を意識している気がしますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In my case… No‚ not just me‚ Nagisa‚ Saki and Mei…\nalso seem to be thinking about Kotono‚ who left.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.8000006358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃を、か……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.9333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "別に、心配しなくていいですわよ？\nこれは決してネガティブな意味ではありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you don't have to be worried.\nIt doesn’t mean anything negative.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2846482204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃が見せてくれていたストイックさ\n美しい歌やダンス、頼りになる背中……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono showed her self-discipline‚\nher beautiful singing and dancing‚ and her reliable presence……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.4000006358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃のこういった姿が、常に私達の頭の片隅にあって\n今でもたまに……支えになってくれますの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These aspects of Kotono have become part of our memories\nand they… still support us even now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.7000006358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……あれだけ長く一緒にやってきたんだから\n琴乃のことを考えるのは自然だよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… You've all been together for a long time‚\nSo it's only natural to think about Kotono",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.5333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "四人になっても……\n私達が琴乃を忘れることなどありませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although it’s just the four of us now…\nWe will never forget Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、そうだよな……。すず、一つ提案なんだが\n琴乃へのその気持ちをテーマにするのはどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ that's right… Suzu‚ I have a suggestion.\nHow about making your feelings for Kotono the theme?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.8000006358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃への気持ちを、曲のテーマに……？\nなるほど……早速、四人で話し合ってみますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "making our feelings for Kotono‚ the theme……?\nOkay… I'll talk with the other members right away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7799.999999999983,
          "startTime": 145.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.0666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 145.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、聞いてくださいまし！\n新曲のテーマが決まりましたの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ please listen!\nThe theme of the new song has been decided!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それって、もしかして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be‚ that……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.0999863942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、琴乃への想いをテーマにしようと提案したら……\n三人は驚きこそしたものの、すぐに賛成してくれました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I suggested making our feelings for Kotono the theme…\nThe others were surprised at first‚ but quickly agreed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "それぞれ抱えていた想いがあったからか\n具体的な言葉も、次々とわいてきましたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe everyone had their own thoughts‚\nso‚ detailed ideas kept coming out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな……どんな意見が出たんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… what kind of ideas did you all come up with?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.7999863942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "四人での活動を通して……琴乃が今までどれほど\n月ストを支えてくれていたか、改めて強く感じたこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Through the activities of just the four of us‚ we strongly felt\nhow much Kotono supported Moon Tempest‚ once again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
