      "text": "もちろん、脱退に加えて移籍希望なんていう\n自分勝手な行動に関しては、腹立たしくもあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I’m still frustrated about\nhow selfish it felt when she quit and changed agencies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
