      "text": "でも……それでも、あの琴乃が選んだ道なら……\n苦しみながらも決めたことなら、背中を押してあげたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… still‚ it's the path Kotono chose…\nIf it was her decision‚ even if it was painful‚ I want to support her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_02-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "そして、そんな琴乃に負けないくらい\n私達も前を向いて、四人でもっともっと輝いてみせる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And‚ the four of us will keep moving forward\nand shine more and more‚ as much as Kotono does.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.8210921171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
